  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>新智元</span> <span>2025-10-22 17:15</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=377c7cd9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14E2eYIgt5nngc2yU2N86AlmZpMORtvHNyYibn7uHMq2T2Rh59ia9S7ojdrjeqkSDGJM61sPGwEnicw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"246\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb15c9CV4Cgm6rMW2FIDGPfLY7FoPDZq847Z67qZQkZfkvibxGdYIX5oCOIQasPBUhEtVhKw53ibxw0g/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-imgfileid=\"505146901\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d5014f41&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb15c9CV4Cgm6rMW2FIDGPfLY7FoPDZq847Z67qZQkZfkvibxGdYIX5oCOIQasPBUhEtVhKw53ibxw0g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;background-color: rgb(127, 127, 127);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;background-color: rgb(127, 127, 127);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;padding: 10px;font-size: 14px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;border-radius: 3px;background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;word-break: break-all !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">短视频的游戏规则，彻底被改写了！9月25日，Meta突然扔出一张新牌——Vibes。刷到的不是别人拍的，而是一条条AI秒生的视频：熊猫骑摩托、猫咪打篮球，你看完还能一键remix，立刻变成你的版本，再发到全网。创作门槛被拉到最低，人人都能拍大片。但这股狂潮，是全民狂欢，还是混乱的开始？&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">9月25日，Meta宣布推出全新功能</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Vibes</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">——一个嵌入在Meta AI应用里的AI视频流。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它不仅能让用户浏览AI生成的短视频，还能一键二创：加音乐、换风格，甚至直接 Remix别人作品，再分享到Instagram和Facebook。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着，短视频的玩法正在被彻底改写。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">过去一年，AI视频工具层出不穷，但大多还停留在小众创作者的实验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Meta的动作，第一次把这类「高门槛」的创作拉进主流社交场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从工具到平台，从个体到社区，Vibes想打造的是一个新的内容循环。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Vibes是什么？</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在Meta最新的公告里，Vibes被定位为「AI视频流」——它不是单纯的工具，而是媒体与创作合体的内容入口。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们正在推出Vibes——一个位于Meta AI应用中心的AI视频流。你可以把自己的想法通过工具变成视频，或remix已有视频，加入音乐、改风格，让它成为你的作品。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更直白地说，Vibes将浏览、创作、分享三个环节打通了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">打开Vibes，你看到的是由AI生成、社区投稿或remix后的视频流，主题多样、风格迥异。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505146812\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.62890625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"364\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=115c0e2d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb15c9CV4Cgm6rMW2FIDGPfLmQIZwp62pX1p3jJLuTfrDicIX50PGK0uNmtcicJNKIX6d9uQ3iajnhTJQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你既可以从空白页开始生成视频，也可以在别人视频基础上remix —— 加音乐、改视觉风格、替换画面元素。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505146820\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8708333333333333\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1920\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1672\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"489\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2b6abac1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb15c9CV4Cgm6rMW2FIDGPfLEFoUBXWggta5uibYvSR361Q04vtnbQNTYcudzjS75TzH3NGhvC00s4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">做好之后，分享也很方便——既能发到Vibes里让更多人刷到，也能私信给朋友，或者一键同步到Instagram、Facebook的Reels和Stories。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更有意思的是，如果你在IG上刷到一条Vibes视频，还能直接跳回Meta AI应用继续remix。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种设计，其实已经透露出Meta的野心：它不满足于给你一个工具，而是想把AI视频变成一种新的日常内容循环。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Meta的野心：在AI视频时代抢回主动权</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">过去几年，短视频已经成为全球社交平台的必争之地。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">TikTok靠着算法推荐和无尽的创意霸占了年轻人的注意力，YouTube也在用Shorts强势追赶，而Meta则把Instagram的Reels推到台前，想要守住阵地。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在Meta自己的战略里，AI从来不是一个边缘实验，而是公司的核心驱动力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">正如扎克伯格在过去的一次访谈中所说：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们会看到更多AI生成内容进入社交平台，内容不再只是朋友、红人在我们的feed中出现，下一阶段的自然形态，是「由你创作」的内容占据主导。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505146819\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6650390625\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1024\" data-height=\"681\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"374\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cad14387&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb15c9CV4Cgm6rMW2FIDGPfLqww6xibnnQPd1Fa2DbpoviciaODt97BoEGI6NibLwMgU1AiawPFCYHvQL2Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">除此之外，Meta在AI研究层面也动作频频。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">旗下团队曾推出名为</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">MovieGen</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">的模型，能生成逼真的视频片段、音频同步，以及在已有视频里做定向修改（比如换背景、加物件）——这套能力正是Vibes所需的技术支撑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">一个由提示词生成的AI视频</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些技术不只停留在研究室，还被快速融入产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Vibes被设计成「刷+改+发」的闭环体验，而不是一个孤立的AI视频工具。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Meta把创作门槛拉低，让普通用户也能触碰AI视频的能力，一旦用户习惯这种玩法，它就可能从工具变成日常。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，Meta本身掌握Instagram、Facebook等强大的内容分发网络。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">把AI视频入口植入它的生态，意味着Meta不必把创作者带到其他平台，而是直接在自己家门口完成流量闭环。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种布局，让Vibes不仅是一个创作入口，也是一张策略王牌。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">当人人都能「拍大片」，原创与二创的边界还在吗？</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Vibes把「刷—改—发」三步变成一个顺滑的闭环，结果是：创作门槛被压到极低。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">过去需要拍摄、剪辑才能做出一条像样的视频，现在只要写几个提示词，点一下remix，就能把别人的灵感变成你的版本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Meta把这一整套流程直接塞进自家App，并打通Instagram、Facebook的分发通道，相当于把AI视频拉进了</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">主流社交舞台</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505146818\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5535307517084282\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"878\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"878\" data-height=\"486\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"311\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=819b3cd7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb15c9CV4Cgm6rMW2FIDGPfLiaxU153EmCBXj6bNe0OvbwhshaqlJ9Tuy6yc4zjMImHXWJzfzRw6Xcw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种现象，在别的平台也初见端倪。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在TikTok上，越来越多账号背后并没有摄影机，只有AI工具：从虚拟主播到批量生成的动漫片段，一条条内容被自动生产出来并推向流量池。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">媒体甚至称之为一种「被动收入」模式，但同时担心会让时间线充斥大量同质化视频。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505146821\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1000\" data-height=\"750\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"422\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d753957a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb15c9CV4Cgm6rMW2FIDGPfLCaQuqOjlhLgU0Wjv5XeUhOE9rTvjsCgJlPLQejY3EQUKF8j1grFbzw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">TikTok也在尝试把AI引入商业场景，比如允许品牌用真人肖像的授权来生成虚拟代言人，快速产出多语言版本广告。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与此同时，争议也越来越尖锐。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI带来的「像谁」「属于谁」的问题已经频繁出现：电商平台曾因推出疑似「AI拟脸」模板，引发创作者强烈反弹，最终不得不紧急下架。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505146822\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1000\" data-height=\"750\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"422\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=97ab0934&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb15c9CV4Cgm6rMW2FIDGPfLoMRJtgJ94cqvD69vUGqwY0iaORIJbVMkDtCQZsTtkMx9ql0gcuKUH4w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这类事件提醒着我们，当remix成为常态，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">版权、肖像权和创作归属</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">都可能变成高频冲突。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">学界对此的担忧也在增加。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">多篇Science等期刊的研究一再强调：当算法推荐与生成式内容结合，虚假信息的传播可能被进一步放大，对平台治理提出更高要求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505146823\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.23091787439613526\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1035\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1035\" data-height=\"239\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"130\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0a1e1781&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb15c9CV4Cgm6rMW2FIDGPfLtqFwzHdwSyhmCzWFSYvuibsMnI2Oibk5ciaJz5Z5q2Y8GNeIib1mewHOag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Science Advances发表的论文《How media competition fuels the spread of misinformation》，指出媒体竞争本身会加速虚假信息传播</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Vibes打开了一扇新门：一方面，它让「人人都能拍大片」成为可能，激活了更多创作灵感；另一方面，它也把平台推到新的临界点——</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">创意和混乱、机会和</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">风险</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，将会同时涌现</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">下一步：从手机屏幕到眼镜</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Vibes只是Meta拼图里的最新一块。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">还有一句话容易被忽略：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Meta&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">应用依然是管理AI眼镜和调用助手的中枢</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着，Vibes并不是一个孤立的功能，而是和硬件、AI助手、社交网络互相串联的节点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">想象一下：戴着Ray-Ban Meta智能眼镜走在街头，说一句「帮我拍个赛博朋克风格的短片」，镜头捕捉下的片段即时被Vibes转化成视频，还能同步发到Instagram Reels。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505146824\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8701612903225806\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1240\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1240\" data-height=\"1079\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"489\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b3d7eb09&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb15c9CV4Cgm6rMW2FIDGPfLOdg1cjMaZ2Q4h82sdkK5LK3UibKBb6dtG4rr6fScYcJeN5bKjkHO1YQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这就不再是「刷别人做的」，而是真正把</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">生成式&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;拉进了现实日常</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">扎克伯格在一次直播中直言：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">智能眼镜会成为未来最自然的计算平台，而AI将是它的核心。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与此同时，AI视频生成本身还在快速迭代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Meta自家的研究团队今年就发布过</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">MovieGen</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型，可以在视频中插入新物体、改背景，甚至保证人物动作和表情的连贯性 。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些底层能力如果逐步融入Vibes，将意味着用户手里的「魔法棒」越来越强。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505146825\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6291666666666667\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1920\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1208\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"354\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df9cbf78&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb15c9CV4Cgm6rMW2FIDGPfL3L3SYTR8icKzPAfKfYFMfbRgdPiaZhVibKmpyMXncvR1ibS7tRHDrEJX6Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当然，未来也不只是技术乐观。伴随而来的问题同样值得警惕：版权归属怎么界定？当生成式内容和真实拍摄混杂在一起，我们还如何判断真伪？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">社交媒体已经在错误信息治理上承压，如今AI视频加入，治理难度只会更高。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可以说，Vibes是Meta在AI时代下的一次「大胆试水」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它可能打开的是一个全新的内容循环，也可能把平台带到新的争议前沿。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但不论如何，这一步已经让我们窥见：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">短视频之后，</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">视频或许正成为下一个全民入口</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">短视频之后，下一个全民入口或许真的就是AI视频。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Vibes让这种想象不再停留在实验室，而是直接进入了我们的社交日常。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从「刷别人」到「改成自己的」，从手机到智能眼镜，Meta正在推动一场新的内容循环。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它让创作更容易，也让传播更迅速，同时也把版权、真伪和治理的难题推到前台。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是一场全民狂欢，也是一场全民考验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Vibes只是起点，真正的变化，才刚刚开始。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://x.com/alexandr_wang/status/1971295156411433228\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/alexandr_wang/status/1971295156411433228</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://about.fb.com/news/2025/09/introducing-vibes-ai-videos/\" target=\"_blank\">https://about.fb.com/news/2025/09/introducing-vibes-ai-videos/</a></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505133683\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2111111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"122\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f15ce8a2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1y6B5OM79TFzpkceWtUkI6LEwv0uYicSoM5Q3I3kDNJhxWdL3tQvbOpU3Ty7icBqnDDNd4CCu4ibiaHw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505123771\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6138888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"355\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d635e771&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1hlU5L2xI2tQx2R2wkgFDYSSrl5MkKQnew6tJZbEl11vWoXJSl8KN49xb9tqpzib1NficyeTibm3pzQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"2652637626\">阅读原文</a></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=e8ba2e80&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzI3MTA0MTk1MA%3D%3D%26mid%3D2652637626%26idx%3D3%26sn%3D53d84ac5433081d5964a02d8665ae810\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Meta 推出 AI 视频流 Vibes，通过降低创作门槛和打通社交分发，试图在 AI 视频时代抢占先机，但也引发版权和虚假信息等争议。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Meta 推出 AI 视频流 Vibes，通过降低创作门槛和打通社交分发，试图在 AI 视频时代抢占先机，但也引发版权和虚假信息等争议。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了 Meta 新推出的 AI 视频流功能 Vibes，该功能嵌入 Meta AI 应用中，允许用户浏览、一键二创（remix）、并分享 AI 生成的短视频到 Instagram 和 Facebook。Vibes 旨在通过极低创作门槛和强大的内容分发网络，改变短视频的玩法，让普通用户也能轻松制作“大片”，从而帮助 Meta 在 AI 视频时代抢回主动权。文章还探讨了 Meta 的野心，指出 Vibes 是其 AI 战略的核心驱动力，并与 Ray-Ban Meta 智能眼镜等硬件生态联动，预示着生成式 AI 将深入日常生活。然而，文章也提出了 Vibes 可能带来的挑战，包括版权归属、肖像权、创作真伪判断以及虚假信息传播等问题，认为这既是全民狂欢也是全民考验。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Meta 推出 Vibes，通过 AI 视频流和一键二创功能，极大降低了短视频创作门槛。",
      "explanation": "Vibes 将 AI 生成、社区投稿和 Remix 功能整合，并打通 Meta 旗下社交平台分发，旨在将 AI 视频创作普及化，吸引普通用户参与。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Vibes 是 Meta 在 AI 时代抢占社交内容主导权的关键策略，并与硬件生态深度整合。",
      "explanation": "Meta 将 AI 视为核心驱动力，Vibes 不仅是内容入口，还与 Meta AI 应用和智能眼镜联动，意图将生成式 AI 融入现实日常，形成新的内容循环。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 视频的普及带来版权、肖像权和虚假信息传播等新的社会治理挑战。",
      "explanation": "当人人都能“拍大片”和 Remix 时，原创与二创的边界模糊，可能导致版权纠纷和虚假信息泛滥，对平台治理提出更高要求。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "刷到的不是别人拍的，而是一条条 AI 秒生的视频：熊猫骑摩托、猫咪打篮球，你看完还能一键 remix，立刻变成你的版本，再发到全网。",
    "我们会看到更多 AI 生成内容进入社交平台，内容不再只是朋友、红人在我们的 feed 中出现，下一阶段的自然形态，是「由你创作」的内容占据主导。",
    "当 remix 成为常态，版权、肖像权和创作归属都可能变成高频冲突。",
    "智能眼镜会成为未来最自然的计算平台，而 AI 将是它的核心。",
    "短视频之后，AI 视频或许正成为下一个全民入口。"
  ],
